<h2>Compare Multiple Lenders</h2>

<p>
Never accept the first mortgage offer you receive. Compare loan estimates
from several banks, online lenders, and mortgage brokers. Even a small
difference in interest rates can save thousands of dollars over the life
of your loan.
</p>

<blockquote>
Shopping around for mortgage rates is one of the easiest ways to save money
without changing your financial situation.
</blockquote>

